  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">FILOXENIA - Temporary Shelter and Protection for the Most Vulnerable Migrants in Greece</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Throughout 2018, Greece continues experiencing an emergency situation related to migration flows and migration management due to the significant number of arrivals, the overstretched accommodation facilities both on the islands and on the mainland and the subsequent protection and safety concerns. Through the present action, IOM will alleviate suffering of vulnerable migrants currently residing under lamentable conditions in Reception and Identification Centers (RICs) by urgently providing dignified accommodation as well as basic assistance and protection services to migrants and refugees residing in accommodation facilities on the mainland, as part of the Government of Greece&#x2019;s overall emergency planning for the decongestion of the reception facilities on the islands.</narrative>
  </description>
